@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### ==========================================
### HEALTH & INFO ENDPOINTS
### ==========================================

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/samples/health

### API Information
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/samples/info

### ==========================================
### PRODUCTS ENDPOINTS (Controllers)
### ==========================================

### Get All Products
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products

### Get Product by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1

### Get Product that doesn't exist (404 demo)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/999

### Create New Product
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "USB-C Cable",
  "price": 19.99,
  "description": "High-speed USB-C charging cable"
}

### Create Product with invalid data (400 demo)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "price": -10,
  "description": "Invalid product"
}

### ==========================================
### ORDERS ENDPOINTS (Controllers)
### ==========================================

### Get All Orders
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders

### Get Order by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/1

### Get Order that doesn't exist (404 demo)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/999

### ==========================================
### PRODUCTS ENDPOINTS (Minimal APIs)
### ==========================================

### Get Products via Minimal API
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/samples/products-minimal

### ==========================================
### DOCUMENTATION
### ==========================================

### Swagger UI (Open in browser - Development only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### OpenAPI JSON Schema
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi/v1.json
